S.FORM: a sinansenay ni kansiungljin (Kán Siōng-jîn) a nakisansemenay mavan aicu a ziyaguitiyaw (Chiaⁿ-goe̍h-tiāu) a senay nua pinairangan. tjemaucikel aicu a senay tua mareka kakudakudan nu semancavilj a sepairang. nu temagilj a pucavilj itjen tjaramedjama itjen a paceged i sangasangasan katua sikamasanmusalj a qadavan. saka nu i sikamasantjelulj a qadavan makaya a kacalaqan. == kasizuanan ==

a sinansenay ni kansiongljin (Kán Siōng-jîn) a nakisansemenay mavan aico a ziyagoitiyaw (Chiaⁿ-goe̍h-tiāo) a senay noa pinairangan. tjemaocikel aico a senay toa mareka kakodakodan no semancavilj a sepairang. no temagilj a pocavilj itjen tjaramedjama itjen a paceged i sangasangasan katoa sikamasanmosalj a qadavan. saka no i sikamasantjelolj a qadavan makaya a kacalaqan. == kasizoanan ==
